0af6f1c3e5b3f9f704b926ca","tid":1822832,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:17:48.000Z","msg":"On9，演練都up得出，夜mama演射槍？<br />\n香港咁撚細，嗰度有人住就一定唔會演練槍。<br />\n原因：巿民聽到唔知者一定會報警，所以唔會喺哩啲地方哩個時候演練，仲要嗌晒：「救命。」<br />\nDklm 幾撚唔合理，當人冇腦。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，警察唔係有座山俾佢哋演練咩，練射tg ar ma，之前有人post過。"},{"pid":"066ca080b79981feb5358b225dc902c29a3048e9","tid":1822832,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}